name: Overline Emblem
description: Overline (https://overline.network) is a blockchain protocol that enables applications built for truly decentralized finance (DeFi), including Overline’s custom, peer-to-peer exchange platform the Interchange. Overline core technology connects disparate blockchains, like Bitcoin and Ethereum, into a unified “multichain”, capable of interoperability and cross-chain communication, all powered by a mineable network and not centralized validators, APIs, or oracles. With no accounts, no wrapped tokens, no personal data, and no exchange/liquidity fees, the Interchange (https://interchange.overline.network) is a first of its kind platform that allows anyone, anywhere to trade wherever and whenever they want.
